name: Liberta Home Seririt Bali
address: Jl. Udayana II Jl. Seririt- Singaraja No.61, Seririt, Kec. Seririt, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81153, Indonesia
review 1: Recomend Hotel  with Affordable price &  exceptional room design, facilites, breakfast. Yoga & Ayunda so friendly, kind and always put smile on everything that they do for us.
review 2: Convenient location of the hotel between the Jalan Seririt - Gilmanuk highway and the ocean. Friendly and hospitable staff. Clean and comfortable room. Clean snow-white linen and towels. I was pleasantly surprised by the presence of an electric kettle, a couple of new toothbrushes with toothpaste in the room. Of the minuses, I will note a very weak water pressure in the shower room and a faulty mechanical soap dish. In the combination of location, hotel room condition, cost and services, I recommend this hotel. Iurii Khmelevskoi
review 3: Clean room, strategic location, excellent services. Strongly recommended for groups touring North Bali
review 4: comfortable, clean with polite staff, and a rooftop heading to beach‚Ä¶, plus fast internet connection & internet tv. üòéüëçüèº
review 5: Suitable hotel to stay in Seririt District. Cozy, clean, afordable room rate with nice, clean, and comfotable room

name: Quick Pizza Delivery Seririt
address: Jl. Seririt- Singaraja No.25, Seririt, Kec. Seririt, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81153, Indonesia
review 1: First time to quick pizza i wanted to send feedback to them but could not find the options. The sauce tasted just like tomato ketchup. Very sweet and sugary. Spoiled the whole thing. Left a strong sweet taste in my mouth. Very unpleasant. The dough was soggy and under cooked. I would not go back. The only pizza that was worse was from berutz and bule. The price was high for local only bule customers in the restaurant. But up to you. If you like over sweet sugary food then this is your place.
review 2: A nice Pizza Place in Seririt-Singaraja, lovely choice of Pizzas, fresh ingredients, fast serving, lovely staff. And they also deliver home. Can highly recommend the Peperoni Pizza. Thank you for having me üôèüèª
review 3: Very good pizza place in seririt ..just what we need here ...takeaways can be a little long wait ..but hey if you want tasty fresh ingredients then you have to wait for perfectionüòâ ...IV just eaten inside ..have to say the service is very good ..great prices ...fantastic pizzas ..try the potatoe mozza ..it's delicious ..thanks quick pizza üçïüôè
review 5: Modern,clean, and very tasty food.  Ticked all my boxes

name: Burger Bangor Seririt
address: Jl. Sudirman No.61, Seririt, Kec. Seririt, Kabupaten Buleleng, Bali 81153, Indonesia
review 1: Didn‚Äôt expect to find both clean and affordable food around that area. This burger is absolutely nourishing and tasty. The price is good too
review 2: It took a long while to prepare our order. The burgers and hotdog where ready quite quick but the fries took another 15minutes. The burgers and hot sat at the pick up point with a fan blowing on them and two bottle of cold coca cola sitting next to them in the bag. By time the fries where added to the bag the coke was not cold and the rest of the food had no heat in at all. If i had not already paid i would have left without paying.
review 3: I ordered two hours ago.. And food not coming..
review 4: Had two cheeseburgers today ..meat very fatty ..need to have better meat ..also they had no french fries ..that's just crazy
